We are Working In Holland, a recruiting company focused on re-locating professionals to work full-time in Holland. Right now, we are looking for professionals who want to relocate to Holland: we will procure excellent, long term working conditions for highly skilled applicants. Our main focus is within IT and Financial sectors, but we are open to candidates from any speciality. You do not need to have an EU nationality, since Holland has programs for highly skilled migrants that make it easy for professionals to obtain working licenses and tax deductions.

For more details, please visit: www.workinginholland.eu
